<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣) حِفْظِ الْمَال الْعَامِّ لِلدَّوْلَةِ، وَيُرَاجَعُ فِي هَذَا مُصْطَلَحِ بَيْتِ الْمَال.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٤) إِقَامَةِ الْعَدْل وَتَنْفِيذِ الأَْحْكَامِ وَقَطْعِ الْخُصُومَاتِ،<span class="c5"> وَيُنْظَرُ فِي ذَلِكَ مُصْطَلَحِ:</span> <span class="c2">(قَضَاء)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> رِعَايَةِ أَهْل الذِّمَّةِ،<span class="c5"> وَيُرَاجَعُ مُصْطَلَحُ:</span> <span class="c2">(أَهْل الذِّمَّةِ)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> تَكْثِيرِ الْعِمَارَةِ،<span class="c5"> وَيُنْظَرُ فِي مُصْطَلَحِ:</span> <span class="c2">(عِمَارَة)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> إِقَامَةِ السِّيَاسَةِ الشَّرْعِيَّةِ،<span class="c5"> وَيُنْظَرُ مُصْطَلَحِ:</span> <span class="c2">(سِيَاسَةٌ شَرْعِيَّةٌ)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>